<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Employee Identity Template</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-3xl bg-white shadow-xl flex flex-col justify-between font-sans mx-auto" style="height:1123px;">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="border-b-8 border-blue-700 pb-4 mb-6 px-8 pt-6 relative">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 tracking-wide">DOTLABS.AI</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">Smart. Simple. Scalable.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-40 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-cyan-400 transform -rotate-2"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="px-8 flex-1 overflow-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 border-b border-blue-500 pb-2 mb-4">Employee Information</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Full Name</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><%= Name %></p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Email Address</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><%= Email %></p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Department</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900"><%= Department %></p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Employee ID</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">#<%= employeeId %></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 p-4 md:p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-4 text-justify">
          <p><%= Name %> has officially been recognized as a trusted and essential part of Dotlabs.ai. As an active contributor in the <%= Department %> department, their role significantly impacts our mission to build intelligent, user-friendly systems that scale efficiently and adapt quickly to evolving needs in the tech world.</p>

          <p>Joining Dotlabs.ai means more than just being part of a company—it means becoming part of a vision to simplify complexity through technology. With each project and every collaboration, <%= Name %> continues to showcase integrity, commitment, and the ability to think beyond the present.</p>

          <p>This document is a formal acknowledgment of the credibility and responsibility entrusted to <%= Name %>. It symbolizes Dotlabs.ai’s gratitude for the consistent performance and passion demonstrated day after day.</p>

          <p>As we move into the future of AI and smart systems, Dotlabs.ai is confident our collective strength lies in people like <%= Name %>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- QR and Footer -->
      <div class="px-8 py-6 relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:absolute md:right-8 md:bottom-24">
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">Scan to verify identity</p>
          <img src="<%= qrCode %>" alt="QR Code" class="w-24 h-24 border-2 border-gray-300 shadow-md">
        </div>

        <footer class="border-t-8 border-blue-700 pt-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-600">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-2 md:gap-8 text-blue-800 mb-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
              <a href="https://www.dotlabs.ai" class="hover:underline">www.dotlabs.ai</a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
              <a href="mailto:career@dotlabs.ai" class="hover:underline">career@dotlabs.ai</a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
              <span>+123 456 7890</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Dotlabs.ai. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>